{"tid":2068383,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"敏感性皮膚嘅你用開邊隻洗面產品？","createTime":"2020-06-17T15:44:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T17:15:00.000Z","uid":190550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"06a14d3d1c96455e002b0da89a6ddb5b04f7027c","tid":2068383,"uid":190550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:44:31.000Z","msg":"我皮膚底弱 好容易敏感<br />\n用親有泡/油狀都會敏感爆粒粒<br />\n而家都係用緊開架醫學品牌洗面乳<br />\n但係潔淨力又唔夠<br />\n所以每次卸妝都要用紅水卸勁多次先敢去洗面<br />\n有冇人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe63b1945d0bbca2df9aed62253965e970c3134","tid":2068383,"uid":69472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:46:41.000Z","msg":"卸妝用油按摩再用洗面奶洗<br />\n我都係敏感皮膚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d869d374cc4cd9575506bc8f35a19f5cb3edddf1","tid":2068383,"uid":307619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:48:21.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"73121f4e7b9bed6fd285833f82dd05268faca02a","tid":2068383,"uid":303698,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:49:01.000Z","msg":"洗面嘅唔覺得有邊款特別好用，但係fancl卸妝油堅好用"},{"pid":"3f15b14d2a6e2e0a6357891f04b4ffcce4b862ca","tid":2068383,"uid":99172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:51:30.000Z","msg":"化少啲妝 <br />\n轉哂所有護膚品做醫美牌子標榜比敏感肌用嗰啲"},{"pid":"12a752d7dfc6a68e2cf1ae60dc94c87952da2758","tid":2068383,"uid":172375,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:52:16.000Z","msg":"敏感肌 建議唔好用水劑落妝 入面啲活性介質會令你啲皮膚愈敏感 建議用gel狀落妝<br />\n洗面建議用ezskin 台灣牌子 但要搵人代購"},{"pid":"09fd540c72975cf9e8a8a3ed05006ead5bc40b21","tid":2068383,"uid":190550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"73121f4e7b9bed6fd285833f82dd05268faca02a","tid":2068383,"uid":303698,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:49:01.000Z","msg":"洗面嘅唔覺得有邊款特別好用，但係fancl卸妝油堅好用"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:52:44.000Z","msg":"我用過fancl <br />\n好俾心機乳化<br />\n但係第二日都係爆哂暗粒同勁紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410d8c0aa0906c6e43a961389057e39ddf860431","tid":2068383,"uid":190550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12a752d7dfc6a68e2cf1ae60dc94c87952da2758","tid":2068383,"uid":172375,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:52:16.000Z","msg":"敏感肌 建議唔好用水劑落妝 入面啲活性介質會令你啲皮膚愈敏感 建議用gel狀落妝<br />\n洗面建議用ezskin 台灣牌子 但要搵人代購"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:53:53.000Z","msg":"Gel狀會唔會卸唔乾淨？有冇邊隻卸妝gel可以推介吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd171aa226cbc05a43b4c99d9fa2e4d0577b1ba","tid":2068383,"uid":250104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:54:19.000Z","msg"